headline: GoDaddy (GDDY): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: GoDaddy has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 8.7%. The stock now trades at $173.99, marking a 13.8% gain. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
